import requests,re
html=requests.get('https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/e/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde.cxg/', timeout=10).text
m=re.search(r'<script src="(static/main-[^"]+\.js)"', html)
print('main js', m.group(1) if m else None)
jsurl='https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/e/21d3e683-80a4-4d9b-bc89-ebb2df513dde.cxg/'+m.group(1)
js=requests.get(jsurl, timeout=10).text
print('js len', len(js))
for pat in ['api.cellxgene', 'datasets', 'dp/v', 'corpora', 'curation', 'schema', 'annotations', 'cell_type']:
    print(pat, js.find(pat))
# print some surrounding text near api.cellxgene
idx=js.find('api.cellxgene')
print('around api', js[idx-100:idx+200] if idx!=-1 else 'none')
# find base urls
urls=set(re.findall(r'https?://[^"\']+', js))
print('num urls', len(urls))
for u in sorted([u for u in urls if 'cellxgene' in u])[:20]:
    print(u)
